## 7. Git Workflow for the Team

```bash
# Each member works on their own branch
git checkout -b feature/knowledge-capture     # Your branch
git checkout -b feature/ai-engine             # AI Engineer
git checkout -b feature/backend-api           # Backend Dev
git checkout -b feature/frontend-ui           # Frontend Dev

# Commit often
git add .
git commit -m "feat: add ttl_checker and quota_tracker functions"

# Push and open PR to main
git push origin feature/knowledge-capture
```

**Branch naming convention:**
- `feature/knowledge-capture` — your module
- `feature/ai-engine` — Groq + HuggingFace RAG
- `feature/backend-api` — FastAPI routes + database.py
- `feature/frontend-ui` — React components
- `feature/api-integration` — SerpAPI connector scripts